name: Brighid, Jewel of Mor Ardain - Xenoblade 2 (Character)
description:
This is a LORA of the character Brighid from the Monolith Soft JRPG Xenoblade Chronicles 2.

To prompt this character, enter "<lora:Brighidv1:strength>Brighid, purple long dress, jeweled collar, accessory belt, closed eyes, closed mouth,". To prompt her holding her whipswords, enter "dual wielding, holding swords," Can be prompted with a 3D aesthetic using "3D Model".

This LORA looks the best at 0.7 ~ 0.8 strength in my opinion. Brighid was trained on AnythingElsev4.5 at Clip Skip 2. This version is far more flexible than v1, and is capable of a very wide range of generations!

modelVersions.name: v1R
trainedWords: Optional: Fiery Hair Buns / Forehead Mark
modelVersions.description: Flexibility fixes, slight dataset quality upgrade. Unlike in v1, Brighid is far more customizable!
